summary: Scientific researcher with a decade of experience at the point of transition from astronomical big data to the projects which have more direct impact on society. Extensive experience in designing and carrying out scientific projects: formulating problems and objectives, finding novel solutions, writing reports and academic papers, communicating findings. Avid learner with meticulous attention to details and the penchant for visual data interpretation.
